# wizcli

Control your WiZ light from the CLI.

## Install

```bash
pip install wizcli
```
## Use

```bash
# turn on
wiz on

# turn off
wiz off

# dim to 20%
wiz dim 20

# set temp to 50%
wiz temp 50

# set cold
wiz cold

# set warm
wiz warm

# set RGB color
wiz rgb 255 40 90
```

